3hs.title: Author's guide to Arbital
3hs.clickbait: How to use Arbital to write the best content?
3hs.text:
Welcome to Arbital. You are probably doing math. You need an invite code.

Arbital is a lot like Wikipedia, but with extra stuff. To read more about how we compare: [1sl]

Working collaboratively together as a community

Arbital is somewhat complex, but this guide will teach you the basics: https://arbital.com/learn/Arbital_author_basics

How to deal with feedback: https://arbital.com/learn/Arbital_author_feedback

More advanced features: https://arbital.com/learn/Arbital_author_advanced
